OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA rather cloudy day for most,
OL,6,Fpatchy rain in the west slowly moving
OL,7,Feast and weakening. Winds increasing
OL,8,Fthrough the day, breaking up the cloud
OL,9,Fto allow some brighter spells this
OL,10,Fafternoon. Further rain arriving in
OL,11,Fthe west by evening.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FA band of heavy rain and
OL,14,Fstrong winds will move eastwards
OL,15,Fovernight. The rain clearing the east
OL,16,Fby morning, allowing some clearer
OL,17,Fspells and a few showers to follow.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
