OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA drier and brighter day
OL,6,Ffor all with a mix of cloud and sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Scattered showers in the north
OL,8,Fand northwest. Winds gradually easing
OL,9,Fand temperatures near average.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
